            "description": "Dengue is a mosquito-borne viral infection causing severe flu-like symptoms.",
            "recommendations": [
                "Drink papaya leaf juice and stay very well hydrated",
                "Use only Paracetamol"
            ],
            "precautions": [
                "Keep mosquitoes away with nets or repellents",
                "Avoid fatty or spicy foods"
            ],
            "symptoms": [
                "high fever",
                "joint pain",
